ygData.subject: Re: Boat problems
ygData.msgSnippet: No, you don t need Jig to swim, but Jig will ensure that your yellow bar will not go all the way down... Lulen ... drown. ... can t ... memorize ... this
ygData.messageBody:
No, you don't need Jig to swim, but Jig will ensure that your 'yellow bar'
will not go all the way down...

Lulen

>
> Huh? Ok. But you dont need Jig to swim. With or without it you won't
drown.
>
> Codo the Mysterious wrote:
>
> > From: "Codo the Mysterious" <codo@...>
> >
> > > docks and dont worry if your yellow bar goes all the way down, you
can't

> > > from swimming as long as you stay on top of the water.

> > That's why he should be a bard who took the time to purchase and
memorize

this
> > song...
